Jiang Wen -LRB- born 5 January 1963 -RRB- is a Chinese film actor , screenwriter , and director .
As a director , he is sometimes grouped with the `` Sixth Generation '' that emerged in the 1990s .
Jiang is also well known internationally as an actor , having starred with Gong Li in Zhang Yimou 's debut film Red Sorghum -LRB- 1986 -RRB- , and more recently as Baze Malbus in the Star Wars anthology film Rogue One -LRB- 2016 -RRB- .
He is the older brother of fellow actor Jiang Wu .